These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-3-1::.
4 different games are played: monopoly, go, backgammon, chess
There 4 different types of food: apple, banana, grapes, pineapple
There are 4 different favourite colors: lilac, amber, black, blue
The people use 4 different means of transport: quad-bike, ship, tram, van
 1. the person eating banana is on the left or right of the person driving the ship##3
 2. the person playing go is the person eating pineapple##1
 3. the person driving the quad-bike is on the far left or far right##3
 4. the person driving the tram is on the right of the person playing go##1
 5. the person driving the quad-bike is on the far left or far right##3
 6. the person eating grapes is on the left or right of the person who likes lilac##3
 7. the person playing backgammon is on the left of the person playing go##1
 8. the person playing chess is on the right of the person eating grapes##1
 9. the person driving the quad-bike is on the far left##1
10. the person who likes black is on the right of the person who likes amber##1
11. the person who likes amber is on the left of the person playing monopoly##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |     2      |      3      |   4   |
| Game    | backgammon   | go       | monopoly | chess   |
| Food        | banana    | pineapple  | grapes      | apple |
| Color         | blue      | amber | black         | lilac   |
| Transport   | quad-bike | ship       | tram        | van   |

