.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-3-2::.
There 4 different types of food: artichoke, peach, cranberry, radish
There are 4 different nationalities: australian, indian, malaysian, turkish
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: ice-hockey, rowing, soccer, tennis
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: november, october, may, august
1. the person who's sport is soccer is on the left of the person who's sport is rowing##1
2. the person eating peach is the australian##1
3. the person who's birthday is in may is the person eating cranberry##1
4. the person eating artichoke is between the indian and the person who's birthday is in november##2
5. the person who's birthday is in november is on the left of the person who's birthday is in october##1
6. the person who's sport is tennis is the person who's birthday is in august##1
7. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the far right##1
8. the person who's birthday is in november is on the far left or far right##3
9. the indian is on the left of the turkish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |       3        |      4       |
| Food           | peach | artichoke | radish | cranberry |
| Nationality   | australian  | malaysian | indian         | turkish      |
| Sport         | soccer      | rowing    | tennis         | ice-hockey   |
| Birthday     | november         | october    | august          | may         |

