The people prefer 4 different music-genres: folk, gospel, indie, rock
4 different pets are kept: cat, dog, hedgehog, turtle
There are 4 different nationalities: spanish, italian, nigerian, japanese
 1. the fan of indie is the nurse##1
 2. the fan of folk is on the far left or far right##3
 3. the electrician is on the left or right of the nigerian##3
 4. the owner of the hedgehog is on the right of the italian##1
 5. the owner of the turtle is on the left of the fan of rock##1
 6. the italian is on the left or right of the japanese##3
 7. the fan of folk is on the left of the spanish##1
 8. the owner of the cat is between the nigerian and the fan of gospel##2
 9. the electrician is on the left of the police-officer##1
10. the photographer is on the left or right of the electrician##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |      3      |     4      |
| Job          | photographer | electrician  | police-officer | nurse      |
| Music-Genre   | folk       | rock    | gospel      | indie      |
| Pet           | turtle     | cat     | dog         | hedgehog   |
| Nationality         | nigerian | spanish | italian     | japanese |

