6. the person who's sport is surfing is on the far left or far right##3
7. the owner of the rabbit is on the left of the owner of the snake##1
8. the person driving the trike is between the owner of the chinchilla and the person who's sport is parkour##2
9. the person driving the bike is on the left or right of the owner of the snake##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |     3     |      4       |
