The people prefer 4 different types of sport: badminton, basketball, cycling, ice-hockey
 1. the person who's sport is badminton is on the left or right of the person traveling to san-francisco##3
 2. the person traveling to paris is on the left or right of the person traveling to rome##3
 3. the person driving the car is on the left of the person traveling to boston##1
 4. the person traveling to paris is on the right of the person traveling to rome##1
 5. the person driving the roller is on the left of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
 6. the person driving the roller is on the far left or far right##3
 7. the fan of funk is on the left or right of the person traveling to paris##3
 8. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left of the person traveling to san-francisco##1
 9. the person traveling to boston is on the left of the person who's sport is basketball##1
10. the fan of trance is between the person driving the car and the fan of reggae##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2      |     3     |     4      |
| Transport      | roller | car | jet-ski     | subway       |
| City          | rome   | paris    | boston | san-francisco       |
| Music-Genre   | funk     | metal       | trance    | reggae     |
