4 different pets are kept: cat, lizard, mouse, rabbit
House: gothic-revival, farmhouse, victorian, wooden
 1. the person who's sport is basketball is on the left of the victorian house##1
 2. the victorian house is on the left or right of the owner of the cat##3
 3. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left or right of the person who's sport is basketball##3
 4. the owner of the rabbit is on the far right##1
 5. the wooden house is between the person who's sport is surfing and the person who's sport is water-polo##2
 6. the person who's sport is basketball is on the right of the owner of the lizard##1
 7. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left or right of the person who's sport is handball##3
 8. the owner of the rabbit is the farmhouse house##1
 9. the owner of the cat is on the left or right of the person who's sport is surfing##3
10. the person drinking fanta is on the far right##1
11. the owner of the lizard is the person who's sport is surfing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |   2    |      3      |     4      |
| Beverage    | soy-milk   | coffee | almond-milk | fanta      |
