 7. the owner of the mouse is between the person who likes yellow and the owner of the bird##2
 8. the fan of pop is the person who's birthday is in april##1
 9. the fan of gospel is on the right of the person who likes lavender##1
10. the person who likes brown is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in december##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |    3     |      4       |
| Birthday         | march | december     | january  | april |
