.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-3-20::.
There 4 different types of food: artichoke, blueberry, radish, watermelon
There are 4 different favourite colors: emerald, grey, turquise, brown
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: adventure, comedy, mystery, satire
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: azalea, begonia, tulip, sunflower
 1. the person eating artichoke is on the far right##1
 2. the person who growsbegonia is on the right of the person who likes emerald##1
 3. the person eating blueberry is on the left of the person eating watermelon##1
 4. the person who likes grey is between the person who growstulip and the person who growsbegonia##2
 5. the person watching adventure movies is on the left or right of the person eating radish##3
 6. the person watching adventure movies is between the person who likes grey and the person who growsazalea##2
 7. the person watching mystery movies is the person who likes brown##1
 8. the person watching mystery movies is on the right of the person watching satire movies##1
 9. the person eating radish is the person who likes grey##1
10. the person watching adventure movies is the person who likes turquise##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2       |    3     |     4     |
| Food          | blueberry | watermelon   | radish   | artichoke |
| Color           | emerald   | turquise     | grey   | brown |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy    | adventure    | satire   | mystery   |
| Flower         | azalea    | begonia | sunflower | tulip    |

 